{% extends 'base.html.twig' %}

{% block title %}About Us - My Arcane Compendium{% endblock %}

{% block body %}
    <div class="about-section">
        <h2>About My Arcane Compendium</h2>
        <p>Welcome to My Arcane Compendium! Our blog is dedicated to exploring the fascinating world of magic, mysticism, and ancient wisdom. We believe in the power of knowledge and the endless curiosity that drives us to uncover the secrets of the universe.</p>

        <h3>Our Mission</h3>
        <p>Our mission is to create a space where enthusiasts of magic and mysticism can come together to share insights, learn from each other, and delve into the mysteries that have captivated humanity for centuries. We aim to provide high-quality content that is both informative and engaging, covering a wide range of topics from historical accounts to modern interpretations of magical practices.</p>

        <h3>Meet the Team</h3>
        <p>Our team is composed of passionate individuals with diverse backgrounds in magic, history, and storytelling. Each member brings their unique perspective and expertise to the table, contributing to the rich tapestry of content that you will find on our blog.</p>

        <h3>Contact Us</h3>
        <p>If you have any questions, comments, or just want to share your thoughts, feel free to <a href="{{ path('contact_page') }}">contact us</a>. We would love to hear from you!</p>
    </div>
{% endblock %}
